\b\fs40         \ul Project Title \ulnone  :   Online Shopping System \par
\b0\fs22\par
\b\i\fs40 1.   \ul  introducation  \ulnone :\b0\fs28\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 Online shopping has become very popular in recent years. People prefer to buy products from the internet instead of visiting physical stores because it saves time and effort. An online shopping system allows customers to search, select, and purchase products through a website. Customers can view product details, compare prices, and place orders from their homes.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}The purpose of this project is to develop a user-friendly online shopping website where \par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}users can browse products, add items to a cart, and place orders easily. The system will also allow administrators to manage products, orders, and customer information.\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\i0\fs40 2. \ul  Problem Statement \ulnone :\ul\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\ulnone\b0\i\fs28 Many small businesses do not have an online platform to sell their products. Because of this, they lose many potential customers who prefer online shopping. Traditional shopping methods also require customers to visit physical stores, which can be time-consuming and inconvenient.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Therefore, there is a need for a simple and efficient online shopping system that allows customers to buy products online and helps businesses manage their sales digitally.\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\i0\fs40 3 .\ul  Objectives of the Project  \ulnone  :\b0\fs28\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\i The main objectives of the online shopping system are:\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}To develop a web-based platform for online product purchasing\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}To allow users to browse and search for products easily\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}To provide a shopping cart for selecting multiple products\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}To allow users to place orders online\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}To provide an admin panel for managing products and orders\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}To create a secure and user-friendly system\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\i0\fs40  4. \ul Scope of the Project\ulnone   :\b0\fs28\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 The online shopping system will provide the following features:\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}User registration and login\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Product listing and product details\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Search and category filtering\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Shopping cart system\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Order placement\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Order management\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Admin panel for product management\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Customer information man\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\par
\b\fs40 5\b0 . \ul\b Proposed System  \ulnone  :\b0\fs28\par

